This market will resolve to "Over" if Keon Coleman records 22 or more receiving yards in regulation and overtime combined.

This market will resolve to "Under" if Keon Coleman records fewer than 22 receiving yards in regulation and overtime combined.

Receiving yards are based on official NFL statistics. If the player does not play or is inactive, this market will resolve to "Under".

If the game is postponed, this market will remain open until the game has been completed. If the game is canceled entirely, with no make-up game, this market will resolve 50-50.

The resolution source will be the official NFL game book as published on NFL.com.
